172
00:08:14,110 --> 00:08:15,860
Okay. Keep me company then.

173
00:08:16,860 --> 00:08:17,490
Come on.

174
00:08:29,280 --> 00:08:30,570
Thanks for the bike.

175
00:08:30,650 --> 00:08:31,490
