213
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,650
Grandpa, don't be mad.

214
00:09:58,780 --> 00:09:59,780
Here, have some more tea.

215
00:09:59,860 --> 00:10:00,990
Okay, okay okay.  -Have some more.

216
00:10:01,110 --> 00:10:02,150
