226
00:10:20,110 --> 00:10:21,070
You have a girlfriend?

227
00:10:22,780 --> 00:10:23,570
Not me.

228
00:10:24,030 --> 00:10:25,110
That's enough.

229
00:10:25,150 --> 00:10:26,740
Don't try to play dumb here.

230
00:10:26,950 --> 00:10:28,400
